{"tid":2261905,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大灣區平均加薪0.9%至6.8%","createTime":"2020-10-28T16:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T15:20:12.000Z","uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"755a3ca36da6a7b8b282635a679708e2f5ee5edd","tid":2261905,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T16:07:06.000Z","msg":"浸會大學調查發現，粵港澳大灣區平均薪金加幅為0.9%至6.8%，預測明年加幅亦達1.1%至8.8%。<br />\n<br />\n浸會大學聯同四個機構，就粵港澳大灣區薪酬及福利作調查，收回253份機構問卷，分別來自香港、澳門及廣東省等十個大灣區城市，涉及約14萬僱員參與。<br />\n<br />\n調查顯示，去年7月至今年6月，公司平均加薪0.9%至6.8%，當中以廣州的經理級及主任或專業人員的職位加薪幅度最多；薪金調整最少是澳門經理級或以上的職位。<br />\n<br />\n至於明年薪金調整幅度，預測為1.1%至8.8%。香港人才管理協會相信，疫情對本港僱員薪酬的影響或於年底顯現。<br />\n<br />\n香港人才管理協會副會長梁偉佳：「我覺得保就業都有效用的，因為都有十多萬僱主參加了，覆蓋率有150萬至200萬，第一期及第二期合共。可看到大家都忍住了，希望將會反彈，但第二波疫情又來，又未通關，最後會怎樣呢？如果持續，我相信情況12月數據會到谷底。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=410718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410718&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7BBMzzOW1qmypsfK5hxWA9U%3D&h=7b74033b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410718&h=b69b0afb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=410718</a>"},{"pid":"f49fd8a53e90202e637835d1fecce73e88481b89","tid":2261905,"uid":41458,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T16:19:46.000Z","msg":"who cares?<br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"387fb312fa09fb1f81881a1c03b23dc851d3c355","tid":2261905,"uid":6030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T18:46:00.000Z","msg":"+$68"},{"pid":"db1068f7f3ae53327eb2bb16a0838b2d571faae8","tid":2261905,"uid":100638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"387fb312fa09fb1f81881a1c03b23dc851d3c355","tid":2261905,"uid":6030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T18:46:00.000Z","msg":"+$68"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T19:55:04.000Z","msg":"Per year"},{"pid":"832d2c7